data.description: Three bedrooms plus an office! This perfectly situated home is in a neighborhood tucked between downtown Granby and Granby Ranch ski mountain. True one story living with this beautifully finished home. Vaulted ceilings in the open concept great room create a warm Colorado entertaining space. Gas fireplace with stone surround. Modern kitchen with updated stainless appliances includes slab granite, designer paint, and solid wood cabinets. French doors lead to the office with ample space for desk and storage. The primary suite is complete with a large bedroom, 5 piece en-suite bath with soaking tub and walk in shower. Oversized walk in closet completes this primary suite. Backyard deck access from the bedroom, the perfect set up if you ever wanted to add a hot tub! The property is fully landscaped with a smart water design and native Colorado plant choices to minimize yard maintenance. The HOA dues are $275 per year and it covers the road grading and plowing. Newer hot water heater, roof, washing machine, appliances. Enjoy nearby skiing, ice fishing, and snowmobiling! Included with the sale are the fire pit, curtains, and outdoor barrels along with the blinds, appliances, washer, dryer, and bird baths. Enjoy a year round get away to this mountain community! Taxes are expected to increase in 2024.
